OL,3,CCould social media firms be forced to
OL,4,Cmake content less addictive for under-
OL,5,C16s?
OL,7,FA landmark Bill being introduced to
OL,8,FParliament on Wednesday could see
OL,9,Frestrictions placed on teenagers'
OL,10,Faccess to social media and mobile
OL,11,Fphones.
OL,13,FThe Safer Phones Bill is a private
OL,14,Fmembers' bill being introduced to
OL,15,FParliament by former teacher and now
OL,16,FLabour MP Josh MacAlister.
OL,18,FUnder the proposed law social media
OL,19,Fcompanies could be made to exclude
OL,20,Funder-16s from their algorithms to
OL,21,Fmake content less addictive.
