OL,12,FThe Bill also calls for a legal
OL,13,Frequirement to be introduced to ban
OL,14,Fmobile phones in all schools in
OL,15,FEngland. The previous government
OL,16,Fissued guidance intended to stop the
OL,17,Fuse of mobile phones during the school
OL,18,Fday, but it's not statutory at the
OL,19,Fmoment.
