OL,7,FUnder the plans put forward by
OL,8,FMacAlister, Ofcom would also be given
OL,9,Fa specific mandate to protect
OL,10,Fchildren's interests, and the
OL,11,Fgovernment would also be committed to
OL,12,Freview regulation around the design,
OL,13,Fsupply, and marketing of mobile phones
OL,14,Fby under-16s.
OL,16,FMacAlister, who led an independent
OL,17,Freview into children's social care for
OL,18,Fthe former government, said: "The
OL,19,Fevidence is mounting that children
OL,20,Fdoom scrolling for hours a day is
OL,21,Fcausing widespread harm.
