OL,11,FWhat kind of restrictions are already
OL,12,Fin place?
OL,14,FThe previous government passed the
OL,15,FOnline Safety Act, which has various
OL,16,Fprovisions in it urging online
OL,17,Fplatforms to protect children -
OL,18,Falthough many campaigners say it
OL,19,Fdoesn't go far enough.
